---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="TANVEER | Nature in Neon">
  <section id="about">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">About Me</h2>
    <p>Hi! I'm Tanveer—a nature explorer with a fascination for futuristic aesthetics...</p>
  </section>

  <section id="places" class="mt-10">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Places I've Explored</h2>

    <div class="place">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-medium">The Himalayas (Spiti & Ladakh)</h3>
      <p>In the high-altitude cold deserts of Ladakh and Spiti...</p>
    </div>

    <div class="place">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-medium">Andaman & Nicobar Islands</h3>
      <p>Beneath the surface of Havelock’s reefs...</p>
    </div>

    <div class="place">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-medium">Western Ghats (Kerala & Karnataka)</h3>
      <p>Hiking through rain-soaked jungles in Wayanad and Coorg...</p>
    </div>

    <div class="place">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-medium">Thar Desert, Rajasthan</h3>
      <p>Across Jaisalmer’s golden dunes I rode camels at dawn...</p>
    </div>

    <div class="place">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-medium">Sundarbans Mangroves</h3>
      <p>Paddling through mangrove labyrinths...</p>
    </div>

    <div class="place">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-medium">Meghalaya (Cherrapunji & Mawlynnong)</h3>
      <p>In the “land of clouds,” I walked across living root bridges...</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="contact" class="mt-10">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">Contact</h2>
    <p>📧 <a href="mailto:tanveer@cybernature.blog">tanveer@cybernature.blog</a></p>
    <p>🌐 Instagram: <a href="https://instagram.com/tanveer.explores" target="_blank">@tanveer.explores</a></p>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-10 text-center">
    <p>🌐 Access online:</p>
    <a class="text-cyan-300" href="https://tanveercybernature.netlify.app">https://tanveercybernature.netlify.app</a>
  </section>
</Layout>
